uto:good%2Cw_620/MjA5MDg5MDQ3MTg4NDE2MzU2/mazda-iconic-sp.webp 620w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjA5MDg5MDQ3MTg4NDE2MzU2/mazda-iconic-sp.webp 700w\"/\u003e\u003csource sizes=\"(min-width: 1240px) 700px, (min-width: 675px) 620px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_380/MjA5MDg5MDQ3MTg4NDE2MzU2/mazda-iconic-sp.jpg 380w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjA5MDg5MDQ3MTg4NDE2MzU2/mazda-iconic-sp.jpg 620w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjA5MDg5MDQ3MTg4NDE2MzU2/mazda-iconic-sp.jpg 700w\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Mazda Iconic SP\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/t_share/MjA5MDg5MDQ3MTg4NDE2MzU2/mazda-iconic-sp.jpg\" data-src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjA5MDg5MDQ3MTg4NDE2MzU2/mazda-iconic-sp.jpg\" height=\"900\" width=\"1600\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" itemprop=\"contentUrl url\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/phoenix-picture\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\u003cp itemprop=\"caption\"\u003eMazda Iconic SP interior\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp itemprop=\"author\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMazda\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe debut of the Iconic SP concept has multiple purposes. As well as reminding the general public that it intends to build drivers’ cars, it sheds light on the direction of Mazda\u0026#39;s design, according to a reply that \u003ca href=\"https://www.carscoops.com/2024/12/mazdas-gorgeous-iconic-sp-is-marching-towards-production-step-by-step-says-ceo/\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eCarscoops\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e received from Mazda USA in a past interview.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eMazda USA responded, “Iconic SP is a design study for future Mazda sports cars. Whether it’s an MX-5 Miata, or any other Mazda vehicle, the people who work at Mazda have a lot of passion for driving and encouraging others to also find that passion through the fun of driving cars that we make and will continue to make.”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cphoenix-super-link href=\"https://www.autoblog.com/news/suzukis-new-car-boasts-a-five-star-rating-for-just-8000\" onclick=\"return window.phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" phx-track-id=\"Embed Card Click\"\u003e\u003c/phoenix-super-link\u003e\u003cp\u003eNow that we know the Iconic SP is officially destined to hit the market, it provides context into what Mazda’s design language could look like for future models, beyond the scope of the halo rotary sports car. As for whether that translates into the next-gen Miata or a standalone vehicle like the RX-7 and RX-8 that previously sold alongside the roadster, remains to be seen.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"final-thoughts\"\u003eFinal thoughts\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\"\u003e\u003cphoenix-picture\u003e\u003ca\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1240px) 700px, (min-width: 675px) 620px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_380/MjA5MDg5MDQ3MTkwOTcyMjYw/mazda-iconic-sp.webp 380w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjA5MDg5MDQ3MTkwOTcyMjYw/mazda-iconic-sp.webp 620w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjA5MDg5MDQ3MTkwOTcyMjYw/mazda-iconic-sp.webp 700w\"/\u003e\u003csource sizes=\"(min-width: 1240px) 700px, (min-width: 675px) 620px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_380/MjA5MDg5MDQ3MTkwOTcyMjYw/mazda-iconic-sp.jpg 380w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjA5MDg5MDQ3MTkwOTcyMjYw/mazda-iconic-sp.jpg 620w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjA5MDg5MDQ3MTkwOTcyMjYw/mazda-iconic-sp.jpg 700w\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Mazda Iconic SP\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/t_share/MjA5MDg5MDQ3MTkwOTcyMjYw/mazda-iconic-sp.jpg\" data-src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjA5MDg5MDQ3MTkwOTcyMjYw/mazda-iconic-sp.jpg\" height=\"900\" width=\"1600\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" itemprop=\"contentUrl url\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/phoenix-picture\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\u003cp itemprop=\"caption\"\u003eMazda Iconic SP\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp itemprop=\"author\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMazda\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eFor now, the signs are positive for Mazda. With attractive looks, a modern powertrain, and company passion behind the project, the Iconic SP looks to be a winner. Now I just have one question for the brand: \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWill the lights pop up?\u003c/p\u003e\u003cphoenix-super-link href=\"https://www.autoblog.com/news/whats-up-with-alfa-romeo\" onclick=\"return window.phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" phx-track-id=\"Embed Card Click\"\u003e\u003c/phoenix-super-link\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
